data.description: BACK ON MARKET - NO FAULT TO SELLER — Welcome to your dream, affordable home in the highly desirable Flowery Branch area! Nestled in a private cul-de-sac, this delightful 3-bedroom, 2-bath ranch is a perfect blend of style and comfort. As you step through the front door, be greeted by a bright foyer bathed in natural light that spills throughout the home, elegantly highlighting the luxury vinyl plank flooring. Located just off the foyer, you'll find the spacious primary suite with walk-in closet, double vanities, spa soaking tub & separate shower! Two additional secondary rooms & bath located across the hall, perfect for peeling the kids out of the bed for school. Venture further into the home to discover a spacious family room where loved ones can gather with ease. This area is anchored by a magnificent limestone fireplace, offering not only warmth but also serving as a stunning focal point that effortlessly combines elegance with coziness. Imagine spending chilly fall evenings here, ensconced in comfort with a good book or engaged in delightful conversation. Next, the renovated farmhouse kitchen is nothing short of a chef’s dream. With an expansive farmhouse sink that makes both cooking and cleaning a breeze, this kitchen is ready to handle anything from quick breakfasts to grand dinners. The floating shelves provide a display for your favorite dishware, while the state-of-the-art stainless steel appliances are both sleek and functional. Adjacent to the kitchen, find an expansive mudroom that serves double duty as a convenient laundry room. With ample space to maneuver, this area acts as the home's functional heartbeat where the day’s clutter finds its place, leaving the rest of your home free to embrace serene living. And for those in need of extra space, this ranch offers a delightful surprise. An upstairs bonus room is ready to adapt to your lifestyle, easily transforming into a fourth bedroom for guests or a private office for your work-from-home needs. The flexibility of this space is a testament to the home’s thoughtful design, anticipating and meeting your living requirements with grace and style. Eager to embrace easy living in Flowery Branch? Where warmth meets convenience in a tranquil residential setting, our enchanting 3-bedroom, 2-bath ranch awaits with open arms and sunlit rooms. Welcome home!
